name: Congrats!
description:
Express your best wishes with authentic wood type. Printed by hand on a vintage Vandercook Proofing Press.

Letterpress is an heirloom printing process that creates a unique texture you can see and feel.

A6 size card (4.375 x 6.25").

Blank inside. Matching envelope included.

name: Chickadees
description:
Cheeky chickadees are brought to life in a three-color letterpress design. A special split-fountain inking technique makes the orange-to-yellow gradient possible.

Letterpress is an heirloom printing process that creates a unique texture you can see and feel.

A6 size card (4.375 x 6.25")

Matching envelope included.

name: Dubuque
description:
We love Dubuque and so should you! This postcard features authentic wood type (front) and a vintage metal cut (back). Printed by hand on a Vandercook Proofing Press (in Dubuque, Iowa of course!). 

Letterpress is an heirloom printing process that creates a unique texture you can see and feel.

Dimensions: 4.375 x 6.25"
